creator: Subsplash Inc
descriptionHtml:
Riverside Christian Assembly is a Spirit filled Bible preaching church. We make disciples using each members gifts and by preaching the gospel. This app is filled with powerful messages, informative classes, inspiring videos and a pathway into our congregation. May God bless you and this awesome platform to share His good news.
RCA uses many creative methods to reach the lost. From our free Shudokon Karate to our Dodgeball tournaments, we believe each local church should be uniquely used by God. We have monthly men's and women's fellowships. We also have weekly evangelism, kids club and youth group. We are an active congregation.
We are proud members of the Fellowship of Christian Assemblies. In which we are a non-denominational autonomous church.

The Riverside Christian Assembly App was created with the Subsplash App Platform.
descriptionShort: RiversideChristianAssembly is a powerful congregation pastored by Drew Brattrud

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
This release includes new features, bug fixes, and performance improvements.
New:
- You can now reorder your media downloads to listen in the order you want.
- Media search has been removed from the app header and is now in the left navigation menu.
Improved:
- Messaging now loads faster!
- Better support for Subsplash Live.
Fixed:
- Fixed several issues where push notifications were not opening Messaging correctly.
- Fixed issue where messages were appearing in the wrong channel.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
New in Messaging (if enabled):
- You can send files to one another
- You can mention someone using an @ symbol to notify them directly.
- Channel managers can restrict channel invites to managers
- Managers can also set artwork and descriptions for a group channel
- Administers can set channels to be public for anyone to join

Fixed:
- Media playback now stops when you force close the app
- Fixed a Messaging issue causing link previews to cause the channel to crash
